    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Until the spell ends, you create an invisible, floating magical eye that hovers in the air and sends you visual information. The eye has normal vision, darkvision to a range of 30 feet, and it can look in every direction.</p><p>You can use an action to move the eye up to 30 feet in any direction as long as it remains on the same plane of existence. The eye can pass through openings as small as 1 inch across but otherwise its movement is blocked by solid barriers.</p><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p><strong>Rare: Sharpshooting Arcane Eye.</strong> Until the spell ends, you have advantage on spell attacks you make against targets you can see with the eye. </p>",
